1. Copy library/Cubique folder to your library
2. Enable autoload. Add this line to your index.php:
    Zend_Loader_Autoloader::getInstance()->registerNamespace('Cubique_');
3. Copy public/helpers folder to your public place
4. Create grid object in the controller, set required and optional parameters
5. Include Cubique scripts and jQuery in your view file:
    $this->headScript()->prependFile(ROOT_PATH . '/helpers/js/cubique.js');
    $this->headScript()->prependFile(ROOT_PATH . '/helpers/js/jquery-1.6.4.min.js');
    $this->headLink()->prependStylesheet(ROOT_PATH . '/helpers/css/cubique.css');
6. Echo grid object variable in the view file